  "general_provisions": "This bill amends provisions related to vehicle emissions inspections to enhance the ability to investigate whether an individual has avoided a required emissions inspection.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>allows the Motor Vehicle Division to revoke the vehicle owner's registration if the vehicle owner has provided a false or an improper address to register a vehicle to avoid an emissions inspection;<hr><ltbullet>prohibits the Motor Vehicle Division from registering a motor vehicle if the owner of the motor vehicle fails to pay a civil penalty for registering with a false or improper address;<hr><ltbullet>allows the State Tax Commission to recover costs of investigation or administration of the provisions of this bill; and <hr><ltbullet>makes technical changes.",
